data.description: Welcome home for the holidays! This exquisite four-bedroom, three-bath residence boasts a spacious and inviting open living area. The living room stands out with its charming stone fireplace, creating a cozy focal point. The kitchen is a culinary dream, showcasing a bat-winged island and an additional center island, providing ample cooking space for your culinary adventures. A generously sized open dining area and a dedicated office space add to the functionality of this home. Enjoy the bonus room, perfect for hosting your billiards table. Connected to the bonus room is a dedicated theater space, creating the ultimate cinematic experience right at home. Positioned on a sizable interior lot, the home offers a covered patio space, blending indoor and outdoor living seamlessly.
